Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:51.26,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,とかなんとか言っちゃってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.46,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,言っちゃってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:59.00,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,空虚な自己防衛さ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:05.13,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,you’re just a pretender　あっぷ あっぷ あっぷ あっぷ　shake, shake, shake it up
