Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:30.74,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,こっちがほんもの　勝者　勝者　勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:44.47,IN_JP_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,鏡の中のおまえを暴く
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.44,0:12:32.37,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,你是要把事情搞複雜嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.94,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,小機靈鬼 調整好你的束腰
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.84,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,稍微抬抬下巴 鏡子裡的我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.62,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,相似卻不同的臉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.79,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,漂亮妝容 是誰 double 變貌 charmin’ chemin’ chumin’
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.87,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,真心就不給你看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.22,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,我沒事 沒錯 流個眼淚給你看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.22,0:12:56.24,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,還清醒嗎？我好著呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.80,0:13:01.77,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,虛假的日子流暢溜走
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.81,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,流暢溜走
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.44,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,只為保持事不關己
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.27,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,30,,[1-2,]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.39,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,30,,i am a pretender up, up, up, up, shake, shake, shake it up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.28,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,責問背影的你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.84,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,30,,[hey!]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.84,0:13:21.74,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,30,,the pretender up, up, up, up, shake, shake, shake it up, it up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.53,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,[哎呀呀]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.51,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,蠢傢伙 再見了 loser, loser, loser
