Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.50,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,我 make up, make up, make up, babe
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.46,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,將你跨過
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.15,0:13:36.84,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,30,,hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.69,0:13:56.20,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,謊言繽紛多彩 笑容叮咚作響
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.10,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,真是讓我心癢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.45,0:14:01.78,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,逢場作戲的算法 冷眼相看
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.78,0:14:06.53,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,但總覺得缺點什麼 想不明白
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.53,0:14:10.17,IN_CH_EP13_M3,,0,0,0,,反正已經習慣了
