Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:35.15,IN_JP_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}光と闇を抱いたまま　胸焦がし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:39.60,IN_JP_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}そうさ　すべてに物語がある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:47.90,IN_JP_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}tell me more　tell me more　don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:06.15,IN_JP_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}巡り逢うノイズの中　魂の overdrive
