Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.45,0:23:25.10,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}講給我聽 講給我聽 若它會實現
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.10,0:23:30.25,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}為何 我會如此思念著一個人
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.25,0:23:35.15,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}懷抱著光與暗 焦急的內心
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.15,0:23:39.60,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}沒錯 世間萬物都有故事
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.60,0:23:47.90,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}請繼續講 請繼續講 不要停止
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.85,0:24:06.15,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}雜音循環往復之中 靈魂過載
Dialogue: 1,0:24:07.70,0:24:10.75,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}我會無數次閃耀光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.25,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}走向崩塌 逐漸失去
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.60,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}一直在找尋的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.35,0:24:20.50,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}剎那間的遙遠色彩
Dialogue: 1,0:24:21.15,0:24:31.10,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}若這首詩歌 會在天球上描繪夢想續篇
Dialogue: 1,0:24:32.33,0:24:33.58,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}請別眨眼
Dialogue: 1,0:24:34.40,0:24:39.65,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}我們將會完全解脫
Dialogue: 1,0:24:39.65,0:24:44.25,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}一同歌唱 一同歌唱
Dialogue: 1,0:24:44.25,0:24:52.15,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}彈奏著那破碎的心
Dialogue: 1,0:24:52.15,0:24:54.65,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:54.65,0:24:59.25,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}向著明天前行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:59.25,0:25:04.40,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}美麗的時代
Dialogue: 1,0:25:04.40,0:25:09.10,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}人總是在忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.10,0:25:14.20,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}最終走向消亡
Dialogue: 1,0:25:14.20,0:25:18.90,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}向那世界前行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:25:18.90,0:25:23.95,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}美麗的時代
Dialogue: 1,0:25:23.95,0:25:28.60,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur4}人總是在忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:25:28.60,0:25:36.25,IN_CH_EP13_M4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,1600)\blur4}最終走向消亡
